overview: Jade Baker and Lena Paul are a young engaged couple planning their big day. Since they are starting to feel overwhelmed, they hire a professional wedding planner. When Gia Paige arrives, she sits the girls down to find out exactly what they both want. Married couple Silvia Saige and Serene Siren are putting on the finishing touches for their daughter's wedding day. As they try to establish who is more involved in her life, things get so heated, that it turns into an all out catfight. When Abigail Mac gets the news that the groom's flight is delayed, she knows it's not going to go over well with Adriana Chechik. As predicted, she freaks out. After the bride calms down with Abigail's help, she carefully suggests that maybe this is a sign that Adriana isn't supposed to get married.
title: Holy Matri-Moly!
